SideshowBob

This CD brings back so many great memories to me.I wore out my old cassette that I had of this.I remember first purchasing this on cassette back in 1994,when I was only ten years old,after it just had been released.Every song on here is great.Too bad Country music doesn't sound like this anymore.This album contains the hit singles,"I See It Now","As Any Fool Can See","Texas Tornado" and "If The World Had A Front Porch".The rest of the album is excellent too.My personal favorite song on here has always been "I Got A Feelin'".This was never a single,but I think it should have been.Overall,if you love 90's Country music as much as I do,then you will love this CD.
